- additional ingredients-
1 lb pastina or anelli pasta (add up to 1.5 lb pasta makes it thicker)
Juice of 1 lemon
salt & pepper to taste
parmesan cheese

## Recipe

In your dutch oven - Place ALL dutch oven ingredients listed in the pot and cover with water
Bring to a boil, reduce to a simmer and cover with the lid and let it simmer for 90 minutes to 2 hours

